creator: chris.lindstrom@senecac.on.ca
text:
Under htdocs, the default index.html page for Ethiopia (index.html.et) is
written in Estonian, as is the Estonian page (index.html.ee)

I've noticed this on the Win32 and *.gz bundles.

*.et was not included in 1.3 so I assume that its an extra copy of the Estonian
page, rather than an Ethiopian page, since Ethiopians use numerous languages.
These pages have been dropped in 2.2.
